<div class="usa-grid-full">
  <p>Chemical Laws &amp; Regulations widget provides federal laws and regulations that are related to chemicals that you search on.</p>
  <p>Chemical details and links to relevant laws and regulations are displayed in a modal when the <strong>Search chemicals</strong> button is clicked. To obtain results, this widget is leveraging <a href="https://iaspub.epa.gov/sor_internet/registry/substreg/home/overview/home.do" rel="external" target="_blank">Substance Registry Services (SRS)</a> to find the chemical substance, its synonyms, and other identifiers and to determine applicable laws and regulations. Results are related to either the chemical searched or its synonym.</p>
  <p>For registered users, the widget provides the ability to save chemicals as favorites for easy reference on return visits. Simply click the corresponding <strong>Save to My Chemicals</strong> link or click the heart icon.</p>
</div><!-- @end usa-grid-full for CR -->
